Text: Analysts expect Algonquin Power & Utilities to earn $0.66 per share next year, which means the company should continue to be able to cover its $0.56 annual dividend with an expected future payout ratio of 84.8%.
Cause: Analysts expect Algonquin Power & Utilities to earn $0.66 per share next year
Effect: the company should continue to be able to cover its $0.56 annual dividend with an expected future payout ratio of 84.8%.
